dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Oriented with north to the left. Bar scales in "Milliaria Gallica communia," "Leucae Hispanicae," and "Milliaria Germanica communia." German text on verso. From Blaeu's Atlantis appendix (1630 or 1631 eds.).
